      "text": [
        " شَهَادَةِ اِمْرَأَةٍ حَضَرَتْ رَجُلاً يُوصِي لَيْسَ مَعَهَا رَجُلٌ فَقَالَ \"تُجَازُ فِي رُبُعِ اَلْوَصِيَّةِ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5435 - Hammad ibn ʿIsa narrated from Ribʿi ibn Abdullah from Abu Abdullah Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) regarding the testimony of a woman who was present when a man was making a will, and there was no man with her.\nImam (as) said: \"Her testimony is accepted for one-fourth of the will.\""
        ]
      }
